title: Couple with Heart: Man, Woman, Dark Skin Tone
description: Represents a ropersontic couple consisting of a person and a person, with a heart symbolizing their love and connection. The dark skin tone indicates a specific representation of the individuals.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the couple with heart emoji, showcasing medium-dark skin tones, depicts two figures embracing, with a prominent, glossy red heart floating between them.  The smooth, rounded forms of the individuals and the heart are enhanced by realistic lighting, conveying warmth and deep affection.  This emoji, as rendered on Apple devices, beautifully symbolizes love, partnership, and romantic connection.
